<header>
    <a href="https://travelbookhotels.com/" rel="noreferrer" target="_blank" aria-label="Travelbook Hotels Logo"><img id="logo" src="/images/logo.png" alt="Travelbook Hotels Logo"></a>
    <h1>Travelbook Group Templates</h1>
    <p>We here at The Travelbook Group take great pride in the websites that we create.</p>
    <p>We listen to what it is you want and then use our expertise and past experiences to create something that is unique to you.</p>
    <p>Whether it be a completely new design or ideas taken from another source it does not matter, we know how to make it into something that you will be proud to call your own.</p>
    <h2>Our templates - Your masterpiece</h2>
</header>
<section class="flex-column">
    <div class="flex-row">
        <%websites.forEach(item=>{%>
            <div class="card" style="--bannerColour:<%= item.primaryColour %>">
                <img src="/images/sites/<%= item.imageFileNames[3] %>" alt="Background image for <%= item.name %>" class="cardImg">
                <div class="cardBody">
                    <h3 class="cardTitle"><%= item.name %></h3>
                    <p class="cardText"><%= item.description %></p>
                    <a href="<%= `/site/${item.id}` %>" class="cardLink">View This Template</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        <%})%>
    </div>
</section>